text: Laize-Clinchamps is a commune. It is found in the region Normandy in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2017 and consists of the former communes of Laize-la-Ville (the seat) and Clinchamps-sur-Orne.Arrêté préfectoral 8 September 2016 == References == Category:2017 establishments in France Category:Communes in Calvados
title: Laize-Clinchamps
